        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/global-map-with-country-flags-ecuador-czech-greece-ukraine-russia.jpg" alt="Illustrated world map featuring the flags of Ecuador, Czech Republic, Greece, Ukraine, and Russia pinned to their respective locations" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="0px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#A9A7AF">
